Thank you, @jredrejo.

@camperjett Some of our routes don't have `name` and only have `component` as an identifier. For such routes, we usually create these maps so that we don't need to reference components' names directly from `$router.getRoute`. However, `PROFILE` and `PROFILE_EDIT` routes already have names. Therefore we don't need to use this map anymore at all (no need to map a route name to the same route name).

To sum it up together with @jredrejo's suggestion, I'd suggest removing this map completely and then simply using  `$router.getRoute('PROFILE_EDIT')`, for example.

